{{Top|leg}}
A '''howdah''' was a small curtained cabin framed with [[Lammas/Legends|lammas]] wood, two meters by three, barely larger than the long padded chaise within. The draped canopy was bounded by a polished rail and the curtains, multiple layers of gauzy lace, were as translucent as smoke.

Howdahs would be fastened with bolts to the back of [[ankkox]]s which were used as transportation through the jungles of [[Haruun Kal/Legends|Haruun Kal]].

